stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Triage
    Triage --> Investigate: incident_id, subsystem, risk
    Investigate --> Decide: hypotheses, citations (doc_id / snippet)
    Decide --> Act: plan (safe + restricted)
    Act --> Report: executed + approval_requests
    Report --> [*]

    Triage --> Escalation: low confidence / timeout
    Investigate --> Escalation: no evidence / conflict
    Decide --> Escalation: policy deny
    Act --> Escalation: OPA error/timeout
    Escalation --> Report: escalation_packet
